      "url": "https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/29/meet-everos-an-open-source-markdown-first-agent-memory-runtime-with-hybrid-bm25-vector-retrieval-and-self-evolving-skills",
      "source": "AIHOT · MarkTechPost（RSS）",
